description.p:
According to an aspect, a structure comprises:
a first layer;
a second layer above the first layer and insulated from the first layer;
the first layer comprising:
first layer metal traces positioned according to a design parameter having a first value for the first layer;
the second layer comprising:
second layer metal traces positioned according to a second value for the design parameter for the second layer, the second value different than the first value;
and where:
the second layer metal traces run in a different direction than the first layer metal traces;
a first electrode connecting the first layer metal traces; and
a second electrode connecting the second layer metal traces.

Advantageously, the second conductive traces comprise interleaving capacitor plates of the first polarity and the second polarity, and further comprising:
a third bus that connects the interleaving capacitor plates of the first polarity;
a fourth bus that connects the interleaving capacitor plates of the second polarity;
a first interconnect between the first bus and the third bus; and
a second interconnect between the second bus and the fourth bus.

claim.claim-text:
A structure comprising:
a first layer;
a second layer above the first layer and insulated from the first layer;
the first layer comprising:
first layer metal traces positioned according to a design parameter having a first value for the first layer;
the second layer comprising:
second layer metal traces positioned according to a second value for the design parameter for the second layer, the second value different than the first value;
and where:
the second layer metal traces run in a different direction than the first layer metal traces;
a first electrode connecting the first layer metal traces; and
a second electrode connecting the second layer metal traces.
